data.description: The ''friendliest Valencia''--Valencia Lakes--reopens a dazzling new Clubhouse end of year, but just around the corner, you can enjoy your private freeform pool and spacious Madeira home just 30 days after going to contract! Don't let this one get away! The 2400sf 3-BR beauty features '23 Dual-Zone AC; renovated maple/granite SS kitchen w/'23 range, refrigerator, microwave, '22 dishwasher; double-wide 4-door pantry; yard-sized expansion of screened-in paver lanai w/ pool+ '23 motor & filter; Family Rm; abundant closets; split BR floor plan w/ ensuite Primary; crown molding; wood Plantation Shutters in Family & Brkfast Rms; 15 yr. roof; complete accordion shutters; fresh Interior paint, Exterior scheduled Spring '24 (cream/taupe). Cafe, USTA Tennis, Pickleball, Main & Lap Pool are open!
